Lesson for the real fans: BELIEVE 🏆

We started off with a convincing win, but things don’t go to plan. 

5 losses in first 7 matches, and detractors are quick to question the captain’s form, team-balance, management’s choices, critically writing them off.

The venue changes from one country to another. From there on, the team goes on to record 7 wins in a row to enter the playoffs with 18 points at #2 on the points table. 

KKR beat Punjab in QF1 to make it to the final. Five days later, the two teams meet again in the final, in Bangalore
The rest is History. 💫

#KKR #Champions #IPL2014
